               Deines <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb12698">Bruders</rs> oder <del rend="strikethrough"><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ei</del> des <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02629-1"/>Locales<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02629-1">nicht identifizert</note>,
               in dem er die <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02629-2"/><rs type="event" ref="#pmb298917" subtype="implied">Hochzeit</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02629-2"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb12698">Julius Schnitzler</rs> und <rs type="person" ref="#pmb24423">Helene Altmann</rs> heirateten am <ref target="1894-07-08" type="schnitzler-tagebuch" subtype="date-only"/>.</note> feiert.</p><p>Und warum<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chreib<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Du mir nicht? Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <lb/>Dein <lb/><signed>P. G.</signed></p></div>
      </body>
